  DMW boss, Davido has reacted to the latest rape allegation against the founder of Commonwealth of Zion Assembly, COZA, Pastor Biodun Fatoyinbo. Busola Dakolo is the top news on everybody’s feed after she revealed that she had been molested as a teenager. Although it allegedly happened a long time ago, the revelation by the mother of three had caused serious unrest online. Reacting to the story, Davido declared his support for Busola Dakolo on instagram. He expressed that he standing firm with Busola Dakolo. He wrote: “We are all here for you.”  The post Davido Said This About Busola Dakolo’s Rape By COZA Pastor appeared first on . Source: 36Ng